column2: Why emphasize the Diabetes Pedigree Function of 0.25 in predicting Diabetes for a 45-year-old female with a BMI of 26, rather than the same Diabetes Pedigree Function in a 70-year-old male with a BMI of 18?
Predict(Diabetes, Age = 45, Sex = Female, BMI = 26, DPF = 0.25) > Predict(Diabetes, Age = 70, Sex = Male, BMI = 18, DPF = 0.25)
